  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "You can remove the `AutoFlushWrapper`:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/c17cafdb57aea27a0809d53766bd99b30dddc1d7/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/NLog.config#L29\r\n\r\nAnd instead use the NLog ColoredConsole option [autoFlush=\"true\"](https://github.com/NLog/NLog/wiki/ColoredConsole-target)\r\n\r\nWhen using `<targets async=\"true\">` :\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/c17cafdb57aea27a0809d53766bd99b30dddc1d7/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/NLog.config#L12\r\n\r\nThen it automatically enables use of AsyncWrapper for all targets, so there is no need to add them again.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/340abf74723f49b83afca4fa2e241f8302c0f5e1/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/NLog.config#L13-L20\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/c17cafdb57aea27a0809d53766bd99b30dddc1d7/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/NLog.config#L30-L36\r\n\r\nRemember to update all `<rules>` when removing the explicit-async and flush (Change from `file-async` to `file` and from `auto-colored-console-async` to `colored-console`)\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/c17cafdb57aea27a0809d53766bd99b30dddc1d7/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Runner/NLog.config#L71-L72\r\n",
