    "body": "When using `<targets async=\"true\">` then it translates into this:\r\n\r\n```xml\r\n<targets>\r\n    <default-wrapper xsi:type=\"AsyncWrapper\" overflowAction=\"Discard\" timeToSleepBetweenBatches=\"1\" batchSize=\"200\" />\r\n\r\n    ...\r\n</targets>\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou are free to use `<default-wrapper>` instead of using `async=\"true\"`.\r\n\r\nSee also: https://github.com/NLog/NLog/wiki/performance",
